procedureJavascriptCode.code:
let candle = record.current

values.push(candle.close)
if (values.length > period) { values.splice(0, 1) }

variable.high = Math.max(...values)
variable.low = Math.min(...values)

let FH = values.indexOf(variable.high)
let FL = values.indexOf(variable.low)

if (FH > FL) {
	variable.F0 = variable.high
	variable.F0236 = variable.high - (variable.high - variable.low) * 0.236
	variable.F0382 = variable.high - (variable.high - variable.low) * 0.382
	variable.F0500 = variable.high - (variable.high - variable.low) * 0.500
	variable.F0618 = variable.high - (variable.high - variable.low) * 0.618
	variable.F0786 = variable.high - (variable.high - variable.low) * 0.786
	variable.F1000 = variable.high - (variable.high - variable.low) * 1.000
	variable.F1618 = variable.high - (variable.high - variable.low) * 1.618

} else {
	variable.F0 = variable.low
	variable.F0236 = (variable.high - variable.low) * 0.236 + variable.low
	variable.F0382 = (variable.high - variable.low) * 0.382 + variable.low
	variable.F0500 = (variable.high - variable.low) * 0.500 + variable.low
	variable.F0618 = (variable.high - variable.low) * 0.618 + variable.low
	variable.F0786 = (variable.high - variable.low) * 0.786 + variable.low
	variable.F1000 = (variable.high - variable.low) * 1.000 + variable.low
	variable.F1618 = (variable.high - variable.low) * 1.618 + variable.low
}

/* Initialization Code*/

period = 10

values = []

variable.high = 1
variable.low = 0

variable.F0 = 0
variable.F0236 = 0
variable.F0382 = 0
variable.F0500 = 0
variable.F0618 = 0
variable.F0786 = 0
variable.F1000 = 0
variable.F1618 = 0
